name: Conners Test for Adults
description: The Conners rating scale is a questionnaire that asks about things like behavior, work or schoolwork, and social life. The answers show your doctor which ADHD symptoms you might have and how serious they are. They can show how these symptoms affect things like grades, job, home life, and relationships
eligibility: 1 AND (2 OR 3 OR 4) AND ( 5 OR 6 OR 7 OR 8 OR (9 AND 10) ) AND 11
